Apart from giving you amazing photo-ops for your social media news feeds, The Raviz Calicut is a unique venue within the city for both your official gatherings as well as personal functions. Our stylish al-fresco dining destination Pergola is a premium space where you can host your memorable events. Just couple it with some poolside fun and you have a winner of an event!
